Adventures in OpenCL: Part 3
http://enja.org

Constant Memory Structs: Passing parameters to a kernel as a __constant struct

Build:
make a build directory and build the tutorial
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make

execute the example program
./part3.x


NOTES:
excellent explanation of alignment in structs:
